SERVER FINAL
============

Go into root folder.
Type "make"
./TuxBomber_Server [x] to start the game where x is the number of expected clients


TuxBomberClient
===============

Go into root folder
Type "make"
./TuxBomber to start the game

Go into Game Options to specify the IP address of the server.
Start game to enter pending mode, waiting for server to start the game.
Server will only start the game when expected number of clients have joined the server.
Arrow keys to move around, Spacebar to drop a bomb.




NOTE: 

Certain SDL libraries are needed to run this program.
SDL, SDL_image, SDL_mixer, SDL_gfx, SDL_ttf
